content: I think there might be some mistake, I'm pretty sure Emily J. Miller is a real author and "The Whispering Walls" is her recently published novel, I got my copy signed at the event. Anyway, I think what I liked about it was the atmosphere and the characters, it had a very immersive world-building. I'm open to different genres, but I'm in the mood for something with a similar vibe. Do you have any suggestions?
